{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>如果一个图存在一笔画，则一笔画的路径叫做欧拉路，如果最后又回到起点，那这个路径叫做欧拉回路。<p><p>根据一笔画的两个定理，如果寻找欧拉回路，对任意一个点执行深度优先遍历；找欧拉路，则对一个奇点执行dfs，时间复杂度为O(m+n)，m为边数，n是点数。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"一笔画问题 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>欧拉路或欧拉回路,输出一条路径即可。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行n，m，有n个点，m条边，以下m行描述每条边连接的两点。<p>","examples":"<input>5 5\n1 2\n2 3\n3 4\n4 5\n5 1\n</input><output>1 5 4 3 2 1\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1341","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}